  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Real Estate Sales Executive",
  "description": "<h3>Job Summary</h3><p>We are looking for a motivated and enthusiastic <strong>Real Estate Sales Executive</strong> to support our sales team in promoting and selling residential and/or commercial properties. The role is ideal for freshers or candidates with 0–2 years of experience who are keen to build a career in real estate sales. The candidate will assist in lead generation, Road show, Event, customer follow-ups, and closing support.<br /><br />Key Roles & Responsibilities</p><ul><li><p>Assist the sales team in marketing and selling residential/commercial projects</p></li><li><p>Handle inbound enquiries from walk-ins, calls, websites, and digital campaigns</p></li><li><p>Explain project details such as pricing, floor plans, amenities, and payment plans to customers</p></li><li><p>Coordinate and conduct site visits with prospective clients</p></li><li><p>Maintain and update customer data in CRM systems</p></li><li><p>Follow up with leads and nurture prospects through regular communication</p></li><li><p>Support documentation related to bookings, agreements, and customer onboarding</p></li><li><p>Achieve assigned monthly and quarterly sales targets</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with internal teams (CRM, legal, marketing, finance) to ensure smooth sales closure</p></li><li><p>Participate in sales events, exhibitions, and promotional activities</p></li><li><p>Stay updated on market trends, competitor projects, and local real estate regulations<br /><br />Desired Skills & Competencies</p><ul><li><p>Good communication and interpersonal skills</p></li><li><p>Customer-focused and result-oriented mindset</p></li><li><p>Basic understanding of real estate sales concepts (preferred)</p></li><li><p>Ability to build rapport and maintain long-term customer relationships</p></li><li><p>Comfortable working with targets and deadlines</p></li><li><p>Basic computer knowledge (MS Excel, CRM tools, email)</p></li><li><p>Willingness to work on weekends and site locations</p></li></ul></li></ul>",
